WEBVTT

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:02.616
The next time someone uses
the r-word near you,

00:13:02.640 --> 00:13:05.240
I hope you will tell them
how much it hurts.

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:10.800
I hope you will think about getting
involved with Special Olympics.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:15.216
(Applause)

00:13:15.240 --> 00:13:17.920
I would like to leave you
with one final thought.

00:13:19.320 --> 00:13:20.976
Nelson Mandela said,

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:23.800
"Sports has the power
to change the world."

00:13:25.040 --> 00:13:27.896
Special Olympics is changing the world

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:31.496
by transforming
four and a half million athletes